---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import info from '../data/info.json';
---

<Layout title="Komunie — Stara Stacja" description="Przyjęcie komunijne na szczycie Szyndzielni. Menu serwowane lub szwedzki stół, dania dla dzieci i dorosłych. Od 180 zł/os.">
  <Nav />

  <!-- Hero — cinematic with parallax -->
  <section class="relative h-[85vh] min-h-[600px] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('/images/wedding/wedding-62.jpg')] bg-cover bg-center scale-105" id="komunie-hero-bg"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-primary/50 via-primary/30 to-primary"></div>

    <!-- Grain overlay -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.03]" style="background-image: url('data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox=%220 0 256 256%22 xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%3E%3Cfilter id=%22noise%22%3E%3CfeTurbulence type=%22fractalNoise%22 baseFrequency=%220.9%22 numOctaves=%224%22 stitchTiles=%22stitch%22/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width=%22100%25%22 height=%22100%25%22 filter=%22url(%23noise)%22/%3E%3C/svg%3E');"></div>

    <div class="relative z-10 text-center text-white px-6 max-w-4xl">
      <div class="w-px h-16 bg-accent/40 mx-auto mb-8 reveal-line"></div>
      <p class="text-accent-light uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-xs sm:text-sm mb-6 reveal-up">Stara Stacja &middot; Szyndzielnia</p>
      <h1 class="font-heading text-5xl sm:text-6xl md:text-7xl font-bold mb-6 reveal-up reveal-delay-1">
        <span class="text-pl">Komunia<br/><span class="text-accent italic font-normal text-[0.55em]">na Szyndzielni</span></span>
        <span class="text-en hidden">First Communion<br/><span class="text-accent italic font-normal text-[0.55em]">at Szyndzielnia</span></span>
        <span class="text-cs hidden">Svaté přijímání<br/><span class="text-accent italic font-normal text-[0.55em]">na Szyndzielni</span></span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl font-light text-white/60 max-w-lg mx-auto mb-12 reveal-up reveal-delay-2">
        <span class="text-pl">Zorganizuj najbardziej wyjątkową komunię na szczycie góry</span>
        <span class="text-en hidden">Organize the most special communion at the mountain summit</span>
        <span class="text-cs hidden">Uspořádejte nejzvláštnější přijímání na vrcholu hory</span>
      </p>
      <div class="reveal-up reveal-delay-3">
        <a href="#oferta" class="group inline-flex items-center gap-3 text-accent uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-sm font-semibold hover:gap-4 transition-all">
          <span class="text-pl">Zobacz ofertę</span>
          <span class="text-en hidden">See offer</span>
          <span class="text-cs hidden">Zobrazit nabídku</span>
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 rotate-90" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" /></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="absolute bottom-8 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 animate-bounce">
      <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white/40" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3" />
      </svg>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Intro — editorial asymmetric layout -->
  <section id="oferta" class="py-32 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-5 gap-12 md:gap-16 items-center">
      <div class="md:col-span-3 scroll-reveal">
        <div class="w-12 h-px bg-accent mb-6"></div>
        <p class="text-accent uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-xs mb-4">
          <span class="text-pl">Przyjęcie komunijne</span>
          <span class="text-en hidden">Communion reception</span>
          <span class="text-cs hidden">Hostina po přijímání</span>
        </p>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">
          <span class="text-pl">Wyjątkowe miejsce<br/>na <span class="italic text-accent">wyjątkowy</span> dzień</span>
          <span class="text-en hidden">A special place<br/>for a <span class="italic text-accent">special</span> day</span>
          <span class="text-cs hidden">Výjimečné místo<br/>pro <span class="italic text-accent">výjimečný</span> den</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-dark/60 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          <span class="text-pl">Stara Stacja to górna stacja kolejki linowej na Szyndzielnię, położona na 1000 m n.p.m. z panoramicznym widokiem na Beskidy. Profesjonalna obsługa, domowa kuchnia i niepowtarzalny klimat dawnej stacji kolejki linowej to idealne tło dla rodzinnego przyjęcia komunijnego.</span>
          <span class="text-en hidden">Stara Stacja is the upper cable car station on Szyndzielnia, situated at 1,000 m a.s.l. with panoramic Beskid views. Professional service, homestyle cuisine, and the unique atmosphere of a former cable car station create the perfect backdrop for a family communion reception.</span>
          <span class="text-cs hidden">Stara Stacja je horní stanice lanovky na Szyndzielnii, v nadmořské výšce 1 000 m s panoramatickým výhledem na Beskydy. Profesionální obsluha, domácí kuchyně a jedinečná atmosféra bývalé stanice lanovky tvoří ideální kulisu pro rodinnou hostinu po přijímání.</span>
        </p>
        <p class="text-dark/60 leading-relaxed">
          <span class="text-pl">Oferujemy dwa rodzaje menu — serwowane lub w formie szwedzkiego stołu — z oddzielnym menu dla dzieci. Możemy pomóc z organizacją biletów na kolejkę linową oraz zamówieniem tortu.</span>
          <span class="text-en hidden">We offer two types of menu — served or buffet-style — with a separate children's menu. We can help arrange cable car tickets and order a cake.</span>
          <span class="text-cs hidden">Nabízíme dva typy menu — servírované nebo formou švédského stolu — s odděleným dětským menu. Pomůžeme s organizací lístků na lanovku a objednáním dortu.</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="md:col-span-2 scroll-reveal">
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="aspect-[3/4] overflow-hidden">
            <img src="/images/wedding/wedding-31.jpg" alt="Wnętrze Starej Stacji — nakryty stół" class="w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <!-- Price badge -->
          <div class="absolute -bottom-5 -left-4 sm:-left-6 bg-accent text-primary px-6 py-4 font-heading text-lg font-bold shadow-lg">
            <span class="text-pl">od 180 zł/os.</span>
            <span class="text-en hidden">from 180 PLN/pp</span>
            <span class="text-cs hidden">od 180 PLN/os.</span>
          </div>
          <!-- Decorative corner -->
          <div class="absolute -top-3 -right-3 w-16 h-16 border-t-2 border-r-2 border-accent/30"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Menu packages — two dramatic cards -->
  <section class="py-32 px-6 bg-cream-dark relative">
    <!-- Subtle decorative background -->
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-accent/20 to-transparent"></div>

    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-20 scroll-reveal">
        <div class="w-px h-12 bg-accent/30 mx-auto mb-8"></div>
        <p class="text-accent uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-xs mb-4">
          <span class="text-pl">Menu komunijne</span>
          <span class="text-en hidden">Communion menu</span>
          <span class="text-cs hidden">Menu k přijímání</span>
        </p>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-primary">
          <span class="text-pl">Dwa warianty <span class="italic text-accent">do wyboru</span></span>
          <span class="text-en hidden">Two options <span class="italic text-accent">to choose</span></span>
          <span class="text-cs hidden">Dvě varianty <span class="italic text-accent">na výběr</span></span>
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-10">

        <!-- Menu Serwowane -->
        <div class="bg-white relative overflow-hidden group scroll-reveal menu-card">
          <!-- Accent top line with animation -->
          <div class="h-1 bg-accent w-0 group-hover:w-full transition-all duration-700 absolute top-0 left-0"></div>
          <div class="h-1 bg-accent/30 w-full"></div>

          <div class="p-8 lg:p-10">
            <!-- Header -->
            <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-8">
              <div>
                <p class="text-accent uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[10px] mb-2">Premium</p>
                <h3 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-primary">
                  <span class="text-pl">Menu Serwowane</span>
                  <span class="text-en hidden">Served Menu</span>
                  <span class="text-cs hidden">Servírované menu</span>
                </h3>
              </div>
              <div class="text-right">
                <p class="text-accent font-heading text-3xl font-bold">230 zł</p>
                <p class="text-dark/30 text-xs uppercase tracking-wider">
                  <span class="text-pl">/ os.</span>
                  <span class="text-en hidden">/ person</span>
                  <span class="text-cs hidden">/ os.</span>
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="w-full h-px bg-cream-dark mb-8"></div>

            <div class="space-y-6 text-sm">
              <div class="menu-item">
                <h4 class="uppercase tracking-wider text-accent text-[11px] font-semibold mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
                  <span class="w-4 h-px bg-accent/40"></span>
                  <span class="text-pl">Zupa</span>
                  <span class="text-en hidden">Soup</span>
                  <span class="text-cs hidden">Polévka</span>
                </h4>
                <p class="text-dark/60 leading-relaxed pl-6">
                  <span class="text-pl">Aromatyczny rosół domowy długo gotowany na mięsie i warzywach, klarowny, podawany z makaronem i świeżą natką.</span>
                  <span class="text-en hidden">Aromatic homemade broth, slow-cooked with meat and vegetables, clear, served with noodles and fresh herbs.</span>
                  <span class="text-cs hidden">Aromatický domácí vývar, dlouho vařený na mase a zelenině, čirý, podávaný s nudlemi a čerstvými bylinkami.</span>
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="menu-item">
                <h4 class="uppercase tracking-wider text-accent text-[11px] font-semibold mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
                  <span class="w-4 h-px bg-accent/40"></span>
                  <span class="text-pl">Danie główne (dla dorosłych)</span>
                  <span class="text-en hidden">Main course (adults)</span>
                  <span class="text-cs hidden">Hlavní chod (pro dospělé)</span>
                </h4>
                <p class="text-dark/60 leading-relaxed pl-6">
                  <span class="text-pl">Soczysty kawał mięsa wieprzowego w chrupiącej panierce podawany z ziemniakami ziołowymi oraz świeżą, sezonową surówką.</span>
                  <span class="text-en hidden">Juicy pork cutlet in crispy breading served with herbed potatoes and fresh seasonal salad.</span>
                  <span class="text-cs hidden">Šťavnatý vepřový řízek v křupavém obalu podávaný s bylinkovanými bramborami a čerstvým sezonním salátem.</span>
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="menu-item">
                <h4 class="uppercase tracking-wider text-accent text-[11px] font-semibold mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
                  <span class="w-4 h-px bg-accent/40"></span>
                  <span class="text-pl">Danie dla dzieci</span>
                  <span class="text-en hidden">Children's menu</span>
                  <span class="text-cs hidden">Dětské menu</span>
                </h4>
                <ul class="text-dark/60 space-y-1.5 pl-6">
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                    <span class="text-accent/40 mt-2 shrink-0">&#8226;</span>
                    <span>
                      <span class="text-pl">Zupa pomidorowa z chrupiącymi grzankami — łagodna i kremowa</span>
                      <span class="text-en hidden">Tomato soup with crispy croutons — mild and creamy</span>
                      <span class="text-cs hidden">Rajčatová polévka s křupavými krutony — jemná a krémová</span>
                    </span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                    <span class="text-accent/40 mt-2 shrink-0">&#8226;</span>
                    <span>
                      <span class="text-pl">Nuggetsy drobiowe z frytkami i suróweczką</span>
                      <span class="text-en hidden">Chicken nuggets with fries and small salad</span>
                      <span class="text-cs hidden">Kuřecí nugety s hranolky a malým salátkem</span>
                    </span>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <div class="menu-item">
                <h4 class="uppercase tracking-wider text-accent text-[11px] font-semibold mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
                  <span class="w-4 h-px bg-accent/40"></span>
                  <span class="text-pl">Zimna płyta</span>
                  <span class="text-en hidden">Cold platters</span>
                  <span class="text-cs hidden">Studené mísy</span>
                </h4>
                <ul class="text-dark/60 space-y-1.5 pl-6">
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-accent/40 mt-2 shrink-0">&#8226;</span><span><span class="text-pl">Patera serów — klasyczne i delikatne odmiany</span><span class="text-en hidden">Cheese platter — classic and delicate varieties</span><span class="text-cs hidden">Mísa sýrů — klasické a jemné druhy</span></span></li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-accent/40 mt-2 shrink-0">&#8226;</span><span><span class="text-pl">Patera szynek i wędlin — wyselekcjonowane, aromatyczne</span><span class="text-en hidden">Ham and cold cuts platter — selected, aromatic</span><span class="text-cs hidden">Mísa šunek a uzenin — vybrané, aromatické</span></span></li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-accent/40 mt-2 shrink-0">&#8226;</span><span><span class="text-pl">Sałatka caprese — mozzarella, pomidor, bazylia, oliwa</span><span class="text-en hidden">Caprese salad — mozzarella, tomato, basil, olive oil</span><span class="text-cs hidden">Salát caprese — mozzarella, rajče, bazalka, olivový olej</span></span></li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-accent/40 mt-2 shrink-0">&#8226;</span><span><span class="text-pl">Domowy smalec z pieczywem górskim</span><span class="text-en hidden">Homemade lard with mountain bread</span><span class="text-cs hidden">Domácí sádlo s horským chlebem</span></span></li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-accent/40 mt-2 shrink-0">&#8226;</span><span><span class="text-pl">Sałatka z grillowanym kurczakiem w lekkim dressingu</span><span class="text-en hidden">Grilled chicken salad in light dressing</span><span class="text-cs hidden">Salát s grilovaným kuřetem v lehkém dresinku</span></span></li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <div class="menu-item">
                <h4 class="uppercase tracking-wider text-accent text-[11px] font-semibold mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
                  <span class="w-4 h-px bg-accent/40"></span>
                  <span class="text-pl">Deser i owoce</span>
                  <span class="text-en hidden">Dessert & fruit</span>
                  <span class="text-cs hidden">Dezert a ovoce</span>
                </h4>
                <ul class="text-dark/60 space-y-1.5 pl-6">
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-accent/40 mt-2 shrink-0">&#8226;</span><span><span class="text-pl">Patera ciast — trzy rodzaje naszych wypieków</span><span class="text-en hidden">Cake platter — three types of our pastries</span><span class="text-cs hidden">Mísa dortů — tři druhy našich zákusků</span></span></li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-accent/40 mt-2 shrink-0">&#8226;</span><span><span class="text-pl">Patera świeżych owoców — kolorowa kompozycja sezonowa</span><span class="text-en hidden">Fresh fruit platter — colorful seasonal composition</span><span class="text-cs hidden">Mísa čerstvého ovoce — barevná sezonní kompozice</span></span></li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Szwedzki Stół -->
        <div class="bg-white relative overflow-hidden group scroll-reveal menu-card">
          <div class="h-1 bg-primary w-0 group-hover:w-full transition-all duration-700 absolute top-0 left-0"></div>
          <div class="h-1 bg-primary/30 w-full"></div>

          <div class="p-8 lg:p-10">
            <!-- Header -->
            <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-8">
              <div>
                <p class="text-primary/40 uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[10px] mb-2">Classic</p>
                <h3 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-primary">
                  <span class="text-pl">Szwedzki Stół</span>
                  <span class="text-en hidden">Buffet</span>
                  <span class="text-cs hidden">Švédský stůl</span>
                </h3>
              </div>
              <div class="text-right">
                <p class="text-accent font-heading text-3xl font-bold">180 zł</p>
                <p class="text-dark/30 text-xs uppercase tracking-wider">
                  <span class="text-pl">/ os.</span>
                  <span class="text-en hidden">/ person</span>
                  <span class="text-cs hidden">/ os.</span>
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="w-full h-px bg-cream-dark mb-8"></div>

            <div class="space-y-6 text-sm">
              <div class="menu-item">
                <h4 class="uppercase tracking-wider text-accent text-[11px] font-semibold mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
                  <span class="w-4 h-px bg-accent/40"></span>
                  <span class="text-pl">Zupy (w wazach)</span>
                  <span class="text-en hidden">Soups (in tureens)</span>
                  <span class="text-cs hidden">Polévky (v mísách)</span>
                </h4>
                <ul class="text-dark/60 space-y-1.5 pl-6">
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-accent/40 mt-2 shrink-0">&#8226;</span><span><span class="text-pl">Aromatyczny rosół domowy — klasyczny bulion gotowany na mięsie i warzywach</span><span class="text-en hidden">Aromatic homemade broth — classic bouillon cooked with meat and vegetables</span><span class="text-cs hidden">Aromatický domácí vývar — klasický bujón vařený na mase a zelenině</span></span></li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-accent/40 mt-2 shrink-0">&#8226;</span><span><span class="text-pl">Zupa pomidorowa kremowa, aksamitna, z dojrzałych pomidorów</span><span class="text-en hidden">Creamy, velvety tomato soup made from ripe tomatoes</span><span class="text-cs hidden">Krémová, sametová rajčatová polévka ze zralých rajčat</span></span></li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <div class="menu-item">
                <h4 class="uppercase tracking-wider text-accent text-[11px] font-semibold mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
                  <span class="w-4 h-px bg-accent/40"></span>
                  <span class="text-pl">Dania gorące (2 do wyboru)</span>
                  <span class="text-en hidden">Hot dishes (choose 2)</span>
                  <span class="text-cs hidden">Teplá jídla (vyberte 2)</span>
                </h4>
                <ul class="text-dark/60 space-y-1.5 pl-6">
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-accent/40 mt-2 shrink-0">&#8226;</span><span><span class="text-pl">Kurczak w chrupiącej panierce</span><span class="text-en hidden">Chicken in crispy breading</span><span class="text-cs hidden">Kuřecí v křupavém obalu</span></span></li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-accent/40 mt-2 shrink-0">&#8226;</span><span><span class="text-pl">Sakiewki wieprzowe z grzybami</span><span class="text-en hidden">Pork purses with mushrooms</span><span class="text-cs hidden">Vepřové kapsy s houbami</span></span></li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-accent/40 mt-2 shrink-0">&#8226;</span><span><span class="text-pl">Roladka z kurczaka ze szpinakiem</span><span class="text-en hidden">Chicken roulade with spinach</span><span class="text-cs hidden">Kuřecí roláda se špenátem</span></span></li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-accent/40 mt-2 shrink-0">&#8226;</span><span><span class="text-pl">Pieczeń wieprzowa ze śliwką</span><span class="text-en hidden">Roast pork with plum</span><span class="text-cs hidden">Vepřová pečeně se švestkou</span></span></li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-accent/40 mt-2 shrink-0">&#8226;</span><span><span class="text-pl">Pierogi z gęsiną</span><span class="text-en hidden">Dumplings with goose</span><span class="text-cs hidden">Pierogi s husím masem</span></span></li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-accent/40 mt-2 shrink-0">&#8226;</span><span><span class="text-pl">Papryka faszerowana (wege)</span><span class="text-en hidden">Stuffed peppers (vegetarian)</span><span class="text-cs hidden">Plněná paprika (vegetariánská)</span></span></li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <div class="menu-item">
                <h4 class="uppercase tracking-wider text-accent text-[11px] font-semibold mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
                  <span class="w-4 h-px bg-accent/40"></span>
                  <span class="text-pl">Dodatki</span>
                  <span class="text-en hidden">Sides</span>
                  <span class="text-cs hidden">Přílohy</span>
                </h4>
                <p class="text-dark/60 pl-6 leading-relaxed">
                  <span class="text-pl">Ziemniaki gotowane, ziemniaki pieczone, frytki. Surówki: mizeria, seler z rodzynkami, buraczki.</span>
                  <span class="text-en hidden">Boiled potatoes, roasted potatoes, fries. Salads: cucumber, celery with raisins, beetroot.</span>
                  <span class="text-cs hidden">Vařené brambory, pečené brambory, hranolky. Saláty: okurkový, celerový s rozinkami, řepový.</span>
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="menu-item">
                <h4 class="uppercase tracking-wider text-accent text-[11px] font-semibold mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
                  <span class="w-4 h-px bg-accent/40"></span>
                  <span class="text-pl">Danie dla dzieci</span>
                  <span class="text-en hidden">Children's menu</span>
                  <span class="text-cs hidden">Dětské menu</span>
                </h4>
                <p class="text-dark/60 pl-6 leading-relaxed">
